    <p>
The trial of Just Stop Oil activists was meant to keep the jurors in the dark about what was at
stake.  The defendants repeatedly violated the judge's orders to
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/environment/article/2024/jul/12/contempt-gagging-un-intervention-uk-wildest-climate-trial-just-stop-oil">speak
