instead to facilitate its destruction.
<p>
But the defendants' effort was not wasted.  The UN rapporteur for
environmental defenders was there, and his report on the trial
was quite stern.
<p>
Side point: I agree that people do not deserve to be punished for making a Zoom call.  However,
using <a href="/zoom.html"></a> Zoom implies being under the power of that company, and that is
itself a punishment.  They should have used <strong>Mumble</strong> or <strong>GNU
Jami</strong> instead.

