Labour has appointed a <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/article/2024/jul/08/a-shoe-fixing-key-cutting-radical-why-labours-new-prisons-minister-is-perfect-for-the-job">practical radical prison reformer as the
prisons minister</a>.

<p>
  </body>
</html>


