    <base href="https://stallman.org/archives/2024-may-aug.html#5_July_2024_(Presidental_immunity,_US_Supreme_Court)">
  </head>
  <body id="msgFeedSummaryBody" selected="false">
    <p>
The Supreme Court ruled that the president has absolute immunity from criminal prosecution over
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/article/2024/jul/01/trump-immunity-ruling-affect-criminal-cases">official
acts</a>.  This covers some of the things he is accused of doing to steal the 2020 election.
<p>
