  </head>
  <body id="msgFeedSummaryBody" selected="false">
    <p>
The UK's "living accommodation" for asylum seekers on former
Wethersfield air base <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/article/2024/jun/30/hunger-strikes-and-suicide-attempts-as-asylum-seekers-claim-essex-site-is-like-prison">feels like a prison</a>.
