  <body id="msgFeedSummaryBody" selected="false">
    <p>
Wikileaks changed the nature of journalism, but with many organizations now set up to publish
leaks, there may not be
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/media/article/2024/jun/28/you-can-expect-everything-what-next-for-julian-assange-and-wikileaks">a
need for Wikileaks itself</a> to resume doing so.  However, Wikileaks has a reputation for
separating the truth from the disinformation, and that could help the public distinguish the two.

<p>
  </body>
</html>


