<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Microplastics</title>
    <base href="https://stallman.org/archives/2024-may-aug.html#1_July_2024_(Microplastics)">
  </head>
  <body id="msgFeedSummaryBody" selected="false">
    <p>
Microplastics (which includes pieces as big as 5mm, which I would call
milliplastics) have <a href="https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/microplastic-found-in-penis-infertility-sperm-count-erectile-dysfunction">been found in human penises and testes</a>.
It is possible that they are responsible for the world-wide decrease
in human fertility over the past few decades.
<p>
But that is not proved.  The cause could be PFAS.  Or something else.

<p>
  </body>
</html>


